        <updateDate>2019-08-20T17:01:00Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Reducing Opioid Risk Act</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Federal Food, Drug, and Cosmetic Act to expand the authority of the Food and Drug Administration to require a drug manufacturer to inform health care providers about state and federal regulations for controlled substances, including the partial fill option.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
